            "category": "Order Status (WISMO)",
            "tags": "on-hold,why,verification",
            "question": "Why does my order say “On‑Hold”?",
            "answer": "<p>We’re just checking something before it moves—usually a quick address/phone confirm or packaging step. Your tracking link shows the latest. If we need anything, we’ll text or email you right away.</p>",
