            "tags": "country estimate",
            "question": "How long to my country?",
            "answer": "<p>As a guide: KSA ~4–5d, UK/US ~5d, AU/CA ~6d. Some routes are faster, and customs can add time. We’ll keep you updated via your tracking link.</p>",
