            "question": "What does “Exception” mean?",
            "answer": "<p>It’s a temporary stop—often a customs check or local delivery event. You usually don’t need to do anything. We monitor these and will update you. If an item can’t clear, we’ll offer a reship, split shipment, or a refund.</p>",
